<commentary>ratneti || ratnacchāyānāṃ padmarāgādimaṇiprabhāṇāṃ vyatikaro miśraṇam iva prekṣyaṃ darśanīyam ākhaṇḍalasyendrasyaitad dhanuḥkhaṇḍam || etad iti hastena nirdeśo vivakṣitaḥ | purastād agre valmīkāgrād vāmalūravivarāt || "vāmalūraś ca nākuś ca valmīkaṃ puṃnapuṃsakam" ity amaraḥ || prabhavaty āvirbhavati | yena dhanuḥkhaṇḍena te tava śyāmaṃ vapuḥ | sphuritarucinojvalakāntinā barheṇa picchena || "picchabarhe napuṃsake" ity amaraḥ || gopaveṣasya viṣṇor gopālasya kṛṣṇasya śyāmaṃ vapur iva | atitarāṃ kāntiṃ śobhām āpatsyate prāpsyate ||</commentary>

tvayīti | | kṛṣer halakarmaṇaḥ phalaṃ sasyaṃ tvayi |